<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Exortando os Evangelhos</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&family=Roboto&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0e6f6, #e6f0fa);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 3rem;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      color: #34495e;
    }

    .evangelhos-container {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin-bottom: 50px;
    }

    .evangelho-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      border-radius: 25px;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: transform 0.4s, box-shadow 0.4s;
    }

    .evangelho-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.05);
      box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    .evangelho-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -50%;
      left: -50%;
      width: 200%;
      height: 200%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,223,0,0.2), transparent 70%);
      animation: rotateHalo 10s linear infinite;
    }

    @keyframes rotateHalo {
      0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
      100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
    }

    h2 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #1f3d7a;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    button {
      margin-top: 15px;
      background-color: #2980b9;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.2s, background-color 0.3s;
    }

    button:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
      background-color: #1c5980;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-top: auto;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Exortando os 4 Evangelhos</h1>
  </header>

  <div class="evangelhos-container">
    <div class="evangelho-card">
      <h2>Mateus</h2>
      <p id="mateus-quote">“Bem-aventurados os que têm fome e sede de justiça, porque serão saciados.”</p>
      <button id="btn-mateus">Nova Mensagem</button>
    </div>

    <div class="evangelho-card">
      <h2>Marcos</h2>
      <p id="marcos-quote">“Vinde após mim, e eu vos farei pescadores de homens.”</p>
      <button id="btn-marcos">Nova Mensagem</button>
    </div>

    <div class="evangelho-card">
      <h2>Lucas</h2>
      <p id="lucas-quote">“Amai os vossos inimigos, fazei o bem aos que vos odeiam.”</p>
      <button id="btn-lucas">Nova Mensagem</button>
    </div>

    <div class="evangelho-card">
      <h2>João</h2>
      <p id="joao-quote">“Eu sou o caminho, a verdade e a vida.”</p>
      <button id="btn-joao">Nova Mensagem</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    Inspirado nos ensinamentos de Cristo e nos quatro Evangelhos
  </footer>

  <script src="/evangelhos.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
